        <name>app_message_outbox_begin</name>
        <param>
          <type><ref refid="struct_dictionary_iterator" kindref="compound">DictionaryIterator</ref> **</type>
          <declname>iterator</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Begin writing to the Outbox&apos;s Dictionary buffer. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">iterator</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Location to write the <ref refid="struct_dictionary_iterator" kindref="compound">DictionaryIterator</ref> pointer. This will be NULL on failure.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>A result code, including but not limited to <ref refid="group___app_message_1gga695a78c926b20edbb14d7faf5a78c29ea12a6ea49b151222e76cf4b99b7c0c4cc" kindref="member">APP_MSG_OK</ref>, <ref refid="group___app_message_1gga695a78c926b20edbb14d7faf5a78c29eadfb91bdd9c369cc2eb00e019b4cf3846" kindref="member">APP_MSG_INVALID_ARGS</ref> or <ref refid="group___app_message_1gga695a78c926b20edbb14d7faf5a78c29eaad6af2baa488efedd56b17f0ed1e8339" kindref="member">APP_MSG_BUSY</ref>.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>After a successful call, one can add values to the dictionary using functions like <ref refid="group___dictionary_1ga30091feef740732d5d6bc3cf2312642a" kindref="member">dict_write_data()</ref> and friends.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="group___dictionary" kindref="compound">Dictionary</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
